1
00:00:06,868 --> 00:00:11,305
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,372 --> 00:00:14,899
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:14,976 --> 00:00:18,412
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,479 --> 00:00:22,074
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:25,415
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,486 --> 00:00:27,420
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,223 --> 00:00:32,158
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,226 --> 00:00:36,026
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,430 --> 00:00:43,268
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,504 --> 00:00:50,569
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,878 --> 00:00:57,010
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,151 --> 00:01:01,417
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,489 --> 00:01:05,084
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:08,492
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,563 --> 00:01:12,192
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,266 --> 00:01:15,861
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,937 --> 00:01:19,429
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,507 --> 00:01:23,102
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,177 --> 00:01:27,273
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:33,331 --> 00:01:36,664
Well then, Guy.
I'll leave Sasuke to you.

21
00:01:43,975 --> 00:01:44,964
Master Jiraiya...

22
00:01:45,176 --> 00:01:45,904
Hmm?

23
00:01:46,744 --> 00:01:49,679
Be sure to find Mistress Tsunade
and bring her back to...

24
00:01:49,747 --> 00:01:53,478
You bet we'll find her
and bring her right away!

25
00:02:02,927 --> 00:02:08,160
Naruto! I like kids with guts like you!
I'm going to give this to you!

26
00:02:09,567 --> 00:02:11,364
This made Lee stronger...

27
00:02:11,669 --> 00:02:13,432
Huh?! What?! What?!

28
00:02:21,279 --> 00:02:22,075
This is it!

29
00:02:30,622 --> 00:02:32,487
Wow!

30
00:02:32,957 --> 00:02:34,618
They're breathable and
moisture wicking,

31
00:02:34,692 --> 00:02:39,026
and perfectly designed for free movement,
all in a beautiful, stylish package.

32
00:02:39,364 --> 00:02:42,492
You'll notice a difference immediately
if you train with them on!

33
00:02:42,934 --> 00:02:44,629
They're going to grow on you!

34
00:02:45,303 --> 00:02:48,101
Before long, you'll be wanting to
wear them all the time like Lee!

35
00:02:48,172 --> 00:02:50,504
Of course, I have a thing for them, too!

36
00:02:52,377 --> 00:02:55,403
Woooow!

37
00:03:01,452 --> 00:03:03,716
<i>Why couldn't you bring a mirror</i>
<i>or something</i>

38
00:03:03,788 --> 00:03:06,814
<i>instead of carrying around</i>
<i>those things, you dork!</i>

39
00:03:14,966 --> 00:03:16,433
Do you think they'll look good on me?

40
00:03:19,404 --> 00:03:22,601
Don't even think about it.
Get a load of that...

41
00:03:25,043 --> 00:03:26,977
Now that is truly dorky.

42
00:03:37,588 --> 00:03:39,556
Okay! This is the place!

43
00:03:41,893 --> 00:03:43,724
Here?!

44
00:03:43,961 --> 00:03:46,395
<i>The gambling house frequented</i>
<i>by the entire town...</i>

45
00:04:01,646 --> 00:04:04,114
<i>Your target is Naruto, after all.</i>

46
00:04:04,716 --> 00:04:11,554
<i>To abduct Naruto is the No. 1 priority</i>
<i>placed by our organization, Akatsuki!</i>

47
00:04:18,129 --> 00:04:19,027
What's wrong?

48
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:24,795
Pervy Sage... Why are they after me?

49
00:04:28,306 --> 00:04:31,537
You know, don't you, Pervert Sage?
Tell me why...

50
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:42,250
They're not really after you...
They're after what's inside of you.

51
00:04:43,187 --> 00:04:45,849
What on earth is this thing?

52
00:04:48,659 --> 00:04:51,719
It's a horrible demon that
attacked Leaf Village, right?

53
00:04:52,063 --> 00:04:54,122
And was dreaded by all.

54
00:04:54,398 --> 00:04:57,458
So why do they want it so much?

55
00:05:00,605 --> 00:05:02,470
Indeed, the Nine Tailed Fox
is a demon

56
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:04,872
that appears at each critical juncture
throughout the ages

57
00:05:05,176 --> 00:05:08,475
destroying everything in its path...

58
00:05:09,514 --> 00:05:13,848
And people feared it like
an act of nature.

59
00:05:20,792 --> 00:05:23,818
The reason they want that thing...
for what purpose.

60
00:05:24,428 --> 00:05:27,955
Honestly, I can't quite say.

61
00:05:29,867 --> 00:05:33,826
Just that now that Nine Tailed Fox
is sealed up inside of you...

62
00:05:34,505 --> 00:05:40,102
they might be thinking
they want that power in their control.

63
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:44,709
It must be harsh to know

64
00:05:44,782 --> 00:05:47,114
that Ninja like them
would keep coming after you...

65
00:05:47,185 --> 00:05:48,413
But well, that's your destiny!

66
00:05:48,786 --> 00:05:51,721
Now don't you worry,
I'm going to protect

67
00:05:51,789 --> 00:05:55,281
Then there's nothing to do
but hurry up and get stronger! I've got to!

68
00:05:57,461 --> 00:06:01,625
Okay! Let's go find that Tsunade person,

69
00:06:01,699 --> 00:06:05,032
have her save Sasuke
and get down to some serious training!

70
00:06:07,338 --> 00:06:09,203
<i>That's just like this kid...</i>

71
00:06:09,941 --> 00:06:15,880
<i>A New Training Begins.</i>
<i>I Will Be Strong!</i>

72
00:06:22,787 --> 00:06:25,654
Th-This place has the highest antes...!

73
00:06:26,490 --> 00:06:28,025
Don't go fretting over
every little thing!

74
00:06:28,025 --> 00:06:29,083
Let's go!

75
00:06:29,427 --> 00:06:32,555
Oh dear! Please wait!

76
00:06:36,634 --> 00:06:37,293
Hmm?

77
00:06:38,536 --> 00:06:39,662
What?

78
00:06:40,538 --> 00:06:44,065
The beautiful woman you
want to "research" on...

79
00:06:44,275 --> 00:06:46,300
That's this Tsunade person?

80
00:06:46,377 --> 00:06:51,178
Whoa! That's sharp coming from you!
And what about it?

81
00:06:51,582 --> 00:06:56,815
She's part of the Sannin thing
like you, right, Pervy Sage?

82
00:06:56,888 --> 00:06:59,015
Yes, and what of it?

83
00:06:59,924 --> 00:07:01,949
How... old is she?

84
00:07:02,026 --> 00:07:03,220
My age.

85
00:07:04,295 --> 00:07:05,660
Heck, she's an old lady.

86
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:17,498
Yikes!

87
00:07:19,176 --> 00:07:20,006
Huh?!

88
00:07:20,077 --> 00:07:21,704
<i>Th-This woman is...!</i>

89
00:07:30,922 --> 00:07:34,187
Would you mind changing all
of this money into chips for me?

90
00:07:37,028 --> 00:07:39,519
Oh no! She's really going for it!

91
00:07:44,769 --> 00:07:47,829
Just who is this? This lady...

92
00:07:48,072 --> 00:07:49,767
You don't know?

93
00:07:50,308 --> 00:07:52,833
She's that woman with
the famous alias...

94
00:07:52,944 --> 00:07:53,968
Famous alias?

95
00:07:57,114 --> 00:07:59,947
So, well... what kind of person
is this Tsunade like?

96
00:08:00,251 --> 00:08:02,219
Oh, you want to know?

97
00:08:02,286 --> 00:08:03,048
Yeah.

98
00:08:03,621 --> 00:08:04,645
Let's see...

99
00:08:05,856 --> 00:08:07,881
Put simply, she's an unpleasant type.

100
00:08:08,726 --> 00:08:13,163
Besides that, she's a diehard gambler
and her face is known far and wide for it.

101
00:08:13,264 --> 00:08:15,323
Then we should have no problems
finding her!

102
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:17,060
If she's that famous!

103
00:08:17,268 --> 00:08:22,171
She's famous, all right...
Legendary, you might say...

104
00:08:27,411 --> 00:08:29,902
Boss, what's this alias?

105
00:08:30,614 --> 00:08:31,638
The Legendary...

106
00:08:32,316 --> 00:08:33,510
Legendary?

107
00:08:48,466 --> 00:08:51,333
<i>Oh dear! They're all laughing!</i>

108
00:08:58,342 --> 00:08:59,969
- Legendary...
- Legendary...

109
00:09:02,146 --> 00:09:03,204
Sitting Duck!

110
00:09:04,782 --> 00:09:09,048
Yup! But no matter how famous
Legendary Sitting Duck is,

111
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,611
I doubt we'll find her right away.

112
00:09:11,789 --> 00:09:13,381
Why not?!

113
00:09:13,657 --> 00:09:15,716
She hates growing old so much

114
00:09:15,793 --> 00:09:19,058
she's probably used some special Jutsu
to change her appearance.

115
00:09:20,231 --> 00:09:22,256
She's actually 50 years old,

116
00:09:22,333 --> 00:09:24,733
but no doubt she looks like
she did when she was 20...

117
00:09:26,737 --> 00:09:29,535
And not just that,
recently I heard that...

118
00:09:29,607 --> 00:09:34,476
she transforms into her teens or
30s or 40s as the situation calls for

119
00:09:34,545 --> 00:09:37,013
to escape moneylenders.

120
00:09:37,515 --> 00:09:40,882
What?! That's a horrible thing to do!

121
00:09:41,152 --> 00:09:45,316
Tsunade has always loved
to gamble more than anything

122
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:48,759
But she has terrible luck and no skill.

123
00:09:50,528 --> 00:09:53,497
She was always being played
for the Sitting Duck and the name stuck...

124
00:09:53,831 --> 00:09:56,823
Then she was always borrowing money
and skipping out on her debts, too...

125
00:09:59,036 --> 00:10:00,663
Ah, it brings back memories.

126
00:10:00,938 --> 00:10:02,997
This is no time to be
getting all nostalgic!

127
00:10:03,541 --> 00:10:06,203
Tell me, how do you propose
we go about finding her?!

128
00:10:06,544 --> 00:10:07,909
Well...

129
00:10:08,145 --> 00:10:09,772
We may very well have to
put our noses to the ground,

130
00:10:09,847 --> 00:10:11,815
but we're not without our little tricks.

131
00:10:11,982 --> 00:10:17,079
What?! So you have no idea
how long it's gong to take?!

132
00:10:17,288 --> 00:10:19,256
We won't be wasting any time.

133
00:10:20,791 --> 00:10:24,056
All of our time on the road
will be your time.

134
00:10:25,196 --> 00:10:26,288
My time?

135
00:10:26,764 --> 00:10:30,200
Time to make you strong...
Training!

136
00:10:39,477 --> 00:10:40,671
Okay!

137
00:10:41,412 --> 00:10:45,178
No, no... I told you that is definitely out.

138
00:10:45,449 --> 00:10:50,113
I won't be seen walking with someone
dressed like that.

139
00:10:57,462 --> 00:11:01,694
Come on, Pervy Sage!
Let's hurry up and start training!

140
00:11:01,866 --> 00:11:04,130
Now now, don't get ahead of yourself...

141
00:11:04,702 --> 00:11:06,932
The training won't mean anything

142
00:11:07,004 --> 00:11:09,996
unless it's done in the process of
gathering information on Tsunade.

143
00:11:10,141 --> 00:11:12,109
Huh? Gathering information?

144
00:11:16,114 --> 00:11:17,172
In this town.

145
00:11:17,815 --> 00:11:19,578
Wow!

146
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:36,929
Cool! This is my first time
for this kind of thing!

147
00:11:37,168 --> 00:11:38,897
Down time is important, too!

148
00:11:38,970 --> 00:11:40,870
You go have yourself some fun
before we start training.

149
00:11:41,272 --> 00:11:43,502
The festival should continue
for some time.

150
00:11:43,775 --> 00:11:45,834
We'll stay here in this city
for the duration.

151
00:11:46,277 --> 00:11:48,040
We'll train here, too!

152
00:11:48,112 --> 00:11:49,670
All right!

153
00:11:57,355 --> 00:12:01,985
Whoa! That's a fat wallet!
You're rich!

154
00:12:02,059 --> 00:12:04,254
I have quite a bit!

155
00:12:04,328 --> 00:12:06,558
I've saved it little by little
throughout my missions.

156
00:12:07,398 --> 00:12:08,262
Well then!

157
00:12:08,332 --> 00:12:10,027
- Wait! Naruto!
- Huh?

158
00:12:10,368 --> 00:12:12,495
I'll hold on to your wallet for you!

159
00:12:12,603 --> 00:12:14,696
Wh-What do you think you're doing?!

160
00:12:15,139 --> 00:12:17,539
You can spend this much...

161
00:12:18,342 --> 00:12:20,606
What?! Only 300 ryo!

162
00:12:20,812 --> 00:12:22,177
No complaints!

163
00:12:22,446 --> 00:12:26,473
Remember Shinobi must honor
the "Shinobi's Three Taboos"!

164
00:12:26,784 --> 00:12:29,947
Shinobi's Three Taboos...?
What's that?

165
00:12:30,188 --> 00:12:32,019
What?! You don't know!

166
00:12:32,256 --> 00:12:33,848
The "three taboos" are
the three temptations

167
00:12:33,925 --> 00:12:36,621
that will bring Shinobi to ruin!

168
00:12:36,961 --> 00:12:41,591
The three temptations are
booze, women and money...

169
00:12:41,699 --> 00:12:45,396
Oh, then this doesn't really apply
to me all that much!

170
00:12:45,803 --> 00:12:51,241
I'm a minor, so I can't drink yet!
I don't quite get the women thing!

171
00:12:51,375 --> 00:12:53,240
And I worked so hard
to save all that money,

172
00:12:53,311 --> 00:12:54,972
I don't really feel much like using it...

173
00:12:55,179 --> 00:12:58,478
You fool! Don't you underestimate
the desire for money!

174
00:12:58,549 --> 00:13:00,414
Once you start using it,
it goes really fast!

175
00:13:02,053 --> 00:13:04,385
Money has a frightful power.

176
00:13:04,856 --> 00:13:06,687
This Tsunade we are going
to be looking for

177
00:13:06,757 --> 00:13:09,225
has ruined herself over it!

178
00:13:10,695 --> 00:13:13,892
Your desire for women is always
getting the better of you, too, Pervy Sage!

179
00:13:14,232 --> 00:13:16,723
I'm going on
an information gathering mission!

180
00:13:17,068 --> 00:13:19,935
Here, you hold on to my bag for me!

181
00:13:20,404 --> 00:13:21,371
If you get lost,

182
00:13:21,439 --> 00:13:25,034
my tracking SummonsToad
will follow my scent!

183
00:13:30,548 --> 00:13:33,415
<i>He's really just a child after all,</i>
<i>contrary to appearances...</i>

184
00:13:39,290 --> 00:13:42,157
Okay! First, I'll get a little something to eat!

185
00:13:46,397 --> 00:13:48,262
I'll take one order of
octopus dumplings, sir!

186
00:13:48,332 --> 00:13:48,923
Right!

187
00:13:49,567 --> 00:13:51,467
- Potatoes with butter please!
- You got it!

188
00:13:51,969 --> 00:13:54,130
- I want chocolate bananas.
- Right!

189
00:13:54,238 --> 00:13:56,706
- I want apricot candy!
- Thank you!

190
00:13:56,774 --> 00:14:00,210
- I want okonomiyaki too!
- Here you go! Watch out, it's hot!

191
00:14:01,712 --> 00:14:04,237
One extra large order
of fried noodle, sir!

192
00:14:04,649 --> 00:14:07,550
Right... But my you've got
a lot of food there, young man!

193
00:14:07,618 --> 00:14:10,212
You don't plan
to eat it all yourself now, do you?!

194
00:14:10,588 --> 00:14:12,715
Eh? As a matter of fact,
I am gong to eat it all myself.

195
00:14:13,157 --> 00:14:14,522
Oh, um, here you go...

196
00:14:20,264 --> 00:14:22,323
I think I ate a bit too much.

197
00:14:24,235 --> 00:14:26,669
<i>I wonder how everyone is?</i>

198
00:14:28,005 --> 00:14:32,874
<i>Kakashi Sensei... Sasuke... Sakura...</i>

199
00:14:33,978 --> 00:14:37,675
<i>I'm going to train hard every day</i>
<i>and come back stronger.</i>

200
00:14:37,748 --> 00:14:38,976
<i>Just you wait and see!</i>

201
00:14:40,051 --> 00:14:42,884
But before that...
I better work off that meal!

202
00:14:43,621 --> 00:14:45,486
Last one!

203
00:14:47,525 --> 00:14:49,686
- All right! Perfect!
- Oh! Amazing!

204
00:14:51,929 --> 00:14:54,557
That's the fruit of hard training
throwing shuriken.

205
00:15:02,573 --> 00:15:04,370
You stink, sonny!

206
00:15:04,442 --> 00:15:07,172
Hah! Gosh darn it!
Well, just watch this!

207
00:15:08,212 --> 00:15:09,076
Hold it!

208
00:15:09,146 --> 00:15:09,976
Huh?

209
00:15:13,451 --> 00:15:16,249
Attention: Shinobi!
Ninjutsu strictly forbidden!

210
00:15:20,124 --> 00:15:20,886
Thanks now!

211
00:15:25,196 --> 00:15:27,630
You shouldn't try to walk around
with the mask on.

212
00:15:36,807 --> 00:15:38,866
It's Pervy Sage's bank saving book.

213
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:43,038
One, ten, one hundred...

214
00:15:44,882 --> 00:15:47,442
<i>L-Look at all those zeros!</i>

215
00:15:48,019 --> 00:15:51,955
He should be treating me now and then
if he has this much money.

216
00:15:52,623 --> 00:15:53,885
Stingy old geezer!

217
00:15:58,195 --> 00:16:02,222
There's only a little left...
One more stand and that will be it...

218
00:16:05,069 --> 00:16:08,561
Time to make you strong...
Training!

219
00:16:14,578 --> 00:16:20,642
Two grilled squids please, sir!
Make one of those an adult size!

220
00:16:20,785 --> 00:16:23,652
Okay! Someone sent you
to buy some squid, eh?!

221
00:16:23,788 --> 00:16:26,154
I'll throw in a child size for free!
Coming right up!

222
00:16:26,824 --> 00:16:29,190
Hurray for you, sir!
You're a man among men!

223
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:33,196
Oh, you can tell, eh?! All right!
I'll give you the adult one for half price!

224
00:16:33,397 --> 00:16:34,591
Thanks!

225
00:16:36,133 --> 00:16:38,727
Good grief, where did he go to?!

226
00:16:41,806 --> 00:16:44,104
Huh? The voice of Pervy Sage?

227
00:16:47,812 --> 00:16:49,871
Young ladies are so nice.

228
00:16:50,114 --> 00:16:53,948
Oh, Naruto! You've already had
you're fill of the festival?

229
00:17:04,829 --> 00:17:08,458
Repeat those three Shinobi Taboos again!

230
00:17:08,933 --> 00:17:11,834
You're breaking all three at once!
You bastard!

231
00:17:12,069 --> 00:17:13,969
W-Wait, Naruto...

232
00:17:14,038 --> 00:17:15,335
N-No, I won't wait!

233
00:17:15,406 --> 00:17:18,739
You used all my hard saved money!

234
00:17:19,009 --> 00:17:20,943
- Take this and this and this!
- N-Naruto, stop!

235
00:17:21,011 --> 00:17:23,673
I'll pay it all back!
I'm sorry, p please!

236
00:17:23,881 --> 00:17:27,373
You! You!
You made my froggy wallet all flat!

237
00:17:28,252 --> 00:17:31,278
Hey! Look what you did, you urchin!

238
00:17:34,592 --> 00:17:39,120
You stained Leader's designer suit!
You'll have to pay for it!

239
00:17:39,263 --> 00:17:40,992
Fork over 100,000 ryo!

240
00:17:41,265 --> 00:17:44,598
What?! You're telling me
that suit cost 100,000 ryo?!

241
00:17:44,768 --> 00:17:47,236
Yeah, really, that's quite a stretch

242
00:17:47,304 --> 00:17:50,102
to say a dorky suit like that
cost 100,000 ryo.

243
00:17:50,407 --> 00:17:52,136
Are you asking for it?!

244
00:17:52,209 --> 00:17:54,268
You better put a lid on it
if you know what's good for you.

245
00:17:54,879 --> 00:17:57,439
The leader used be a Chunin from
the Hidden Village of Stones,

246
00:17:57,515 --> 00:18:01,417
the legendary dark Ninja, feared by all!

247
00:18:01,819 --> 00:18:05,118
Come again? Legendary what?

248
00:18:05,523 --> 00:18:08,117
You seem to want to get hurt!

249
00:18:09,126 --> 00:18:10,093
Naruto.

250
00:18:11,195 --> 00:18:12,184
Perfect timing.

251
00:18:12,630 --> 00:18:17,090
I'll show you a Jutsu now...
Watch very carefully!

252
00:18:18,035 --> 00:18:19,297
Now you've done it!

253
00:18:28,012 --> 00:18:29,741
A-Amazing!

254
00:18:35,252 --> 00:18:38,688
I was holding back quite a bit...
You guys are so weak.

255
00:18:43,127 --> 00:18:46,858
A-Are you? The... legendary...

256
00:18:47,464 --> 00:18:50,592
I'm sorry...
We kind of destroyed your stand...

257
00:18:51,068 --> 00:18:53,400
H-Here... Fix. It with this.

258
00:18:53,604 --> 00:18:55,697
Oh! Thanks.

259
00:18:56,740 --> 00:19:00,904
Would you mind if I bought all
your balloons and water balloons

260
00:19:00,978 --> 00:19:02,309
at the same time, my man?

261
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,877
Fine by me...

262
00:19:07,451 --> 00:19:09,351
<i>That wasn't an ordinary hand move...</i>

263
00:19:09,753 --> 00:19:12,415
<i>What in blazes was that?!</i>
<i>That Jutsu!</i>

264
00:19:13,057 --> 00:19:13,921
Naruto!

265
00:19:14,792 --> 00:19:17,124
Come with me! It's training time!

266
00:19:18,329 --> 00:19:19,125
Yes, sir!

267
00:19:28,038 --> 00:19:30,700
Finally, the mood is right
for a little training.

268
00:19:31,108 --> 00:19:32,871
- Here! Water balloon!
- Wha?

269
00:19:33,544 --> 00:19:35,603
Eh?! What is it for?!

270
00:19:36,247 --> 00:19:39,273
You saw that Jutsu I just used, right?

271
00:19:39,416 --> 00:19:40,747
Y-Yeah.

272
00:19:40,918 --> 00:19:42,283
What Jutsu did it look like to you?

273
00:19:44,521 --> 00:19:47,354
It looked like you made
your opponent spin violently.

274
00:19:48,292 --> 00:19:50,886
<i>His perspective's off...</i>
<i>But I guess that's to be expected.</i>

275
00:19:52,029 --> 00:19:53,894
Right, okay... Yes, spinning

276
00:19:55,366 --> 00:19:58,961
<i>He's spinning the water in the balloon</i>
<i>without moving his hand?!</i>

277
00:20:02,306 --> 00:20:03,204
Whoa!

278
00:20:03,774 --> 00:20:05,139
The tree climbing exercise

279
00:20:05,209 --> 00:20:07,905
to learn to gather and
maintain Chakra in necessary places...

280
00:20:08,679 --> 00:20:10,237
The Walk on Water exercise

281
00:20:10,314 --> 00:20:12,339
to learn how to release
a set amount of Chakra...

282
00:20:12,916 --> 00:20:15,146
You did both of these, right?

283
00:20:16,020 --> 00:20:18,784
And now with this water balloon exercise,

284
00:20:18,856 --> 00:20:20,721
you'll learn how to create
a stream of Chakra...

285
00:20:21,425 --> 00:20:22,915
In other words, spinning.

286
00:20:23,961 --> 00:20:26,191
Create a stream of Chakra...

287
00:20:26,597 --> 00:20:28,929
I'll give a more detailed explanation
of the Jutsu

288
00:20:28,999 --> 00:20:31,490
once you get these first steps down.

289
00:20:32,269 --> 00:20:34,430
First, you must gather
and maintain Chakra in your hand

290
00:20:34,505 --> 00:20:35,802
using the tree climbing technique.

291
00:20:36,573 --> 00:20:38,097
Then you must continuously
release Chakra

292
00:20:38,175 --> 00:20:40,040
using the Walk on Water technique.

293
00:20:40,811 --> 00:20:45,839
Then you push and churn the water
in the balloon with the Chakra!

294
00:20:46,617 --> 00:20:48,016
I get it!

295
00:20:48,385 --> 00:20:50,717
Then you spin the water
in the balloon faster and faster

296
00:20:50,788 --> 00:20:53,086
until the balloon pops!

297
00:20:53,791 --> 00:20:56,726
You're catching on
more and more quickly!

298
00:20:57,194 --> 00:20:59,594
Okay, today we're going
to train until evening

299
00:20:59,730 --> 00:21:00,594
Yes, sir!

300
00:21:09,607 --> 00:21:13,543
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

301
00:21:14,545 --> 00:21:18,504
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

302
00:21:19,817 --> 00:21:27,781
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

303
00:21:28,759 --> 00:21:30,852
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

304
00:21:33,631 --> 00:21:36,657
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

305
00:21:37,101 --> 00:21:42,038
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

306
00:21:42,173 --> 00:21:47,634
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

307
00:21:47,912 --> 00:21:52,815
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

308
00:21:52,883 --> 00:21:57,786
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

309
00:21:57,855 --> 00:22:07,025
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

310
00:22:07,498 --> 00:22:12,367
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

311
00:22:12,436 --> 00:22:18,272
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

312
00:22:19,910 --> 00:22:30,047
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

313
00:22:37,895 --> 00:22:41,160
I will break this water balloon
no matter what!

314
00:22:41,298 --> 00:22:43,732
Hey, you're full of spirit!

315
00:22:44,835 --> 00:22:46,860
Perhaps I can expect him
to master the Jutsu.

316
00:22:47,972 --> 00:22:50,497
The water inside the balloon
is moving.

317
00:22:52,109 --> 00:22:54,669
By the way, when does that pop?

318
00:22:55,279 --> 00:22:58,442
Next time: "Keep on Training
Pop Goes the Water Balloon!"

319
00:22:58,882 --> 00:23:02,113
Aw geez! Why won't it pop?!
